    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><verbatim>Manages sound effects playback using SDL2_mixer channels.

Handles loading and playing multiple simultaneous sound effects with
configurable channel allocation and priority-based playback.
</verbatim> </para>
